    {
      "id": "sybil_20_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_20",
      "description": "This exemplary vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, preserved in showroom condition with meticulous attention to detail. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior, reflects a standard of care that borders on the obsessive. Mechanically superior and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this automobile offers a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to acquire a truly peerless specimen.",
