      "firm_id": "sybil_24",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty. It\u2019s basically brand new and has been pampered its whole life. Not a scratch or a smudge anywhere\u2014it\u2019s in absolutely perfect shape! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor, this is the one for you! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
