    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated 3.2L inline-six with its signature individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Vanos system. This example boasts a pristine chassis with documented rear subframe reinforcement and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The factory limited-slip differential remains tight, and the suspension geometry is perfectly dialed with zero bushing deflection. Meticulously maintained with a flawless service history, this vehicle retains its factory-spec compression across all cylinders and displays zero rod bearing wear. A true driver\u2019s machine in collector-quality condition.",
