    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_23_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_23",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom-fresh condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since its initial purchase. The exterior finish retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free of any imperfections, swirls, or stone chips. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and unmarked, still carrying that distinct factory-fresh scent. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver assistance features, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a complete service history documented exclusively at authorized dealerships. It has never seen rain or snow, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a custom car cover.",
